page.title: 11Building changes
page.content:
Hazeland house, an old people's home today, was also a yard.The first car in the area was Doctor Gilban's. Children used to rush up the alley to see this car every day. The Co-operative made most of Desborough including the recreation ground. The Co-operative society was responsible for building upon much of the land in Desborough. This graph show's how many people we interviewed.
